name: The Sebben, Sebben, and Birdman E.P. v1.0
description:
The E.P. that I’ve been working on.  This is the first cut of it, so it’s only a 1.00, which will help me cut the cost of producing the finished one.  It’s a CD-R, but I’ll make it nice and sign it. 
It features the songs:

	
1. Every Single Word

2. I’ll Help You

3. Side View

4. Let Me In

5. That’s Why You Always Leave a Note

6. Life Taker (vs. Enigma MC)

7. The West Coast (vs. The Redlight Exchange)

8. Mistake (vs. Jay Tholen)

9. Yesterday (Beatles Cover)

10. Daniel’s Love
